Package org.bukkit.block.data.type

Interface ChiseledBookshelf

All Superinterfaces:
BlockData, Cloneable, Directional
public interface ChiseledBookshelf extends Directional
Interface to the 'slot_0_occupied', 'slow_1_occupied' ... 'slot_5_occupied' flags on a bookshelf which indicate which slots are occupied rendered on the outside.
Block may have 0, 1... getMaximumOccupiedSlots()-1 occupied slots.
